data.description: SELLER WILL LOOK AT ALL OFFERS *PERFECTLY POSITIONED ON 5 ACRES IN MUCH SOUGHT AFTER GATOR CREEK ESTATES * Peaceful & private living * Social distancing at its best * DRIVE UP THE PICTURESQUE WINDING CIRCULAR DRIVEWAY & open the double front doors to a 2 STORY GRAND FOYER & STAIRCASE FEATURING 5 BEDROOMS & 3 BATHS * Split plan design with 3 Guest Bedrooms UPSTAIRS * Owners' Suite is DOWNSTAIRS with an adjacent Den/Office as well as the 5th Bedroom (or Bonus Room) which has no closet (but one could be added) * NEWLY REMODELED KITCHEN IS A BEAUTIFUL CLASSIC DESIGN with ISLAND SEATING, UPGRADED QUARTZ COUNTER-TOPS, SOLID WOOD CABINETS, STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, DOUBLE OVEN & A BUILT-IN WINE COOLER * Kitchen is open to the FAMILY ROOM with WOOD-BURNING FIREPLACE * Formal Living Room & Formal Dining Room * All of this wraps your CAGED POOL THAT IS PERFECT FOR YOU TO ENJOY IN YOUR SLICE OF PARADISE * Very Private Pool * 4 Car Garage + 2 Car Carport * Bring the kids, the toys big & small * Horses are allowed * Make this your family estate * The grounds are beautiful with mature oaks - it's a Myakka State Park-like setting * A-RATED SCHOOLS * Gator Creek is gated at night and 1 mile to Publix & shopping * Just 15 minutes to Siesta Key Beach and the UTC Mall * Country living yet close to town * ONE LOOK & YOU'LL FALL IN LOVE * REALTORS: PLS READ REALTOR REMARKS.
